MPIPerf
-------

MPIPerf is a benchmark for MPI libraries.

Version 0.0.3
* Tests for MPI 3.0 non-blocking collectives are implemented.

Version 0.0.2
* Tests for MPI 2.2 collectives are implemented.

  
For problem reports and suggestions on the implementation, 
please contact:

Mikhail Kurnosov
E-mail: mkurnosov@gmail.com
http://cpct.sibsutis.ru/~mkurnosov
         
